# Master wiki — knowledge map

Reshaped (Task 4.4) to the L2 pointer-map schema (spec §3.1 L2): "a compact per-project page holding general project knowledge plus an index of pointers — a map, not the territory." This file plays that role for the wiki as a whole; per-project maps live at `projects/<slug>/map.md`, assembled by `skills/ingest-project/lib/assemble_l2` (same schema, one map per project).

This file is updated by `/ren:wrap` whenever a session promotes content to the wiki. You can also edit it by hand.

## Knowledge

_General facts about this wiki as a whole will be listed here as they're captured — e.g. "friend prefers X," "this wiki covers N active projects."_

## Decision map

_Pointers into `decisions/`, `patterns/`, `research/`, and per-project maps will be listed here, one per line:_

`- [<topic>] → <wiki-relative-path>#<anchor> (<write_id or "unstamped">)`

